Added regression coverage for dashboard active-task filtering to ensure `not_started` and `in_progress` statuses are counted while `completed`, `cancelled`, and `archived` are excluded. Updated CommandCenter active counts to consistently use `status.isActiveWork` in all dashboard active-count paths.

Test run status: `swift test --filter TaskStatusActiveWorkTests` and `swift test` are currently blocked by pre-existing duplicate test filename collisions in the repo (SwiftPM multiple producers for AIUsageTrackingTests.swift, AgentPickerTests.swift, TaskNotesResizeTests.swift).